{"tid":592532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[出哂水]FT專訪　林鄭大讚習近平：你會話我擦鞋，但他越來越有魅力和令人敬佩","createTime":"2018-03-14T09:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T11:29:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"668ebb1e8b577f5e3a413c12822a0a7f604f9798","tid":592532,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》今日刊出行政長官林鄭月娥的專訪。被記者問到最欣賞哪一位政治領袖時，林鄭向國家主席習近平表示敬意：「你可能會說這是在擦鞋，但我不得不說，我認為習主席在他處事及說話上，越來越有魅力和令人敬佩。」<br />\n<br />\n指年輕人有嫉妒心態<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》的記者在禮賓府與林鄭進行訪問，期間談到本港房屋問題。林鄭表示能夠理解年輕人的挫敗感，並推出了措施協助首次置業的人士。但當談到2014年的佔領運動時，她就指出有年輕人被引導到更激進的立場，是因為有嫉妒的心態：「當其他人擁有它時，為何我不能？」<br />\n<br />\n她表示是受到對香港的熱愛，以及強烈的天主教信仰所驅使，又認為其宗教信仰與她作為無神論共產黨的地方執政者，兩者角色並不存在矛盾。對於在早前競選期間，因不懂用八達通及不懂買廁紙而被網民嘲笑，她表示曾經對這些嘲弄感到不開心和憤怒，但現在已越來越不上心。<br />\n<br />\n她又否認北京正在向香港施壓，認為中國只是堅持捍衛其主權，情況有如西班牙在歐盟支持下處理加泰的情況：「只要我們尊重一國，那麼就能保留自己的制度。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/ft%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%91%E6%93%A6%E9%9E%8B-%E4%BD%86%E4%BB%96%E8%B6%8A%E4%BE%86%E8%B6%8A%E6%9C%89%E9%AD%85%E5%8A%9B-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E6%9C%89%E5%AB%89%E5%A6%92%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fft%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2593%25A6%25E9%259E%258B-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25BB%2596%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25B6%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25AD%2585%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AB%2589%25E5%25A6%2592%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2585%258B%2F&d=dkR71RwkcYhLNLQ6qeEO%2FjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1b6ea8a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fft%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2593%25A6%25E9%259E%258B-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25BB%2596%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25B6%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25AD%2585%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AB%2589%25E5%25A6%2592%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2585%258B%2F&h=9bc714db\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/ft%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%91%E6%93%A6%E9%9E%8B-%E4%BD%86%E4%BB%96%E8%B6%8A%E4%BE%86%E8%B6%8A%E6%9C%89%E9%AD%85%E5%8A%9B-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E9%9D%92%E6%9C%89%E5%AB%89%E5%A6%92%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"d9e52d9170e98d0da2f3a9b6fd28b35b923a27d8","tid":592532,"uid":55581,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老味真係拎加泰黎比喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n9成9唔知加泰歷史同狀況先亂鳩咁up"},{"pid":"ccd81f06be6654a1783945a4fddba13f7ae18ff7","tid":592532,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04b470bdaefb67aa99c000f2461e44ffe5d3af5a","tid":592532,"uid":163758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ccd81f06be6654a1783945a4fddba13f7ae18ff7","tid":592532,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"快同jr攬住死"},{"pid":"5ff6f38293825897cc04cc84da71106aedc81e54","tid":592532,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36223de0a1f87767f4b9521711b70eba5f67ef20","tid":592532,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci